o this transfer for you...
If you opt for advertising, we now get to turn on the ad campaign!  Minimum r=
ecommended is $200/mo.  Best would be around $600/mo.  None is actually nece=
ssary but highly recommended and you can cancel anytime.
The service I'm recommending is a full service package from The HVAC Network=
.  Setup costs $1000 and gets you all your hosting and 24/7 support for a ye=
ar.  Advertising costs will be billed monthly as employed.

The basic deal:
core site setup with up to 10hrs custom work.
24/7 support for a year.
hosting for a year.
build 2 seasonal (summer/winter) landing pages optimized for google adwords
google adwords ad campaign setup
bi-monthly ad campaign tuning for a year (normally $200/mo!)
keyword and service area meta tag optimization for your entire site and land=
ing pages
google map with driving directions on your site
appointment scheduling tool on website
dns transfer services
site monitoring
tools (and training) for you to easily update the content on any of your sit=
es pages via the content management system.
Google analytics configuration
